data.title: Mountlake Terrace
data.meta_description: Learning should be meaningful and fun. New Song Academy is giving children opportunities to explore and experiment helps them become independent and capable initiators of their own learning with christian value of education.
data.text:
Learning should be meaningful and fun. Giving children opportunities to explore and experiment helps them become independent and capable initiators of their own learning. Children should actively involve in their own learning and we believe that the process of learning is more important than the end product.

To take learning a step further than the normal classroom environment, New Song Academy offers an optional Enrichment Classes in the afternoon. These classes and programs include Music, foreign languages, art, STEM, and advanced literature and language program.
